instructions: put the dinner plate in the middle of the table cloth, towards the bottom
place the salad plate directly in the middle of the dinner plate
place the napkin directly in the center of the salad plate
place the wine glass to the top right of the plate, in the north east corner
place the water glass to the right of the wine glass a few inches down
place the salad fork tines up to the left of the dinner plate, an inch from the bottom of the mat
place the dinner fork to the right of the salad fork, tines up, between salad fork and dinner plate
place the dinner knife to the right of the dinner plate, blade pointing up facing the left
place the soup spoon to the right of the knife, bowl facing up
